\section kitchen Doxygen Kitchen Sink

This section, and others like it, can be removed by commenting out the 'ENABLED_SECTIONS = ASEI_INTERNAL'
line in project.doxyfile. Its purpose is to demo useful doxygen commands.

<b>NOTE:</b> If using Qt Creator most of these commands can be autogenerated by typing '/\*\*' + [ENTER]

\subsection fileHeader File Headers
\verbatim
/** @file [<name>]
 * A brief file description.
 * A detailed file description.
 */
 \endverbatim
Typically used for the documentation of global functions, variables, typedefs, and enums.
Output is shown in the Files section of the doygen output. If the file name is omitted then the 
documentation block belongs to the file it is located in.

\subsection classHeader Class Headers
\verbatim
